{"tid":1833970,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[大結局！聽日準時返工]武大中南醫院：以ECMO技術成功救治1患者","createTime":"2020-01-22T07:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:06:34.000Z","uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"41420bd51b0fca98cd718689da626d2bf657a156","tid":1833970,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1686309/即時-中國-武漢肺炎-武大中南醫院-以ECMO技術成功救治1患者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1686309%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%97%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E4%BB%A5ECMO%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%91%E6%B2%BB1%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=66e8b834\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1686309%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%97%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E4%BB%A5ECMO%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%91%E6%B2%BB1%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85&h=818033fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1686309/即時-中國-武漢肺炎-武大中南醫院-以ECMO技術成功救治1患者</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎繼續肆虐。根據內地傳媒報道，武漢大學中南醫院用移動心肺儀（ECMO）成功救治了一名新型冠狀病毒患者，屬全省首例。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述武漢大學中南醫院急危重症移動ECMO中心主任夏劍表示，是次新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情造成患者的肺部受損，成為「病毒肺」，嚴重的患者肺部受損嚴重，影響人體肺部正常工作。醫院利用移動心肺儀（ECMO），在人體外安放一個人工膜肺，替代人的肺的工作，相當於「人工替代肺」，讓人體自身的肺能夠得到充分的治療和休息。病發時的缺氧症狀得到改善，目前已成功救治了一名新型冠狀病毒患者。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，移動心肺儀（ECMO）應用範圍還比較小，現暫時只在中南醫院、金銀潭醫院等武漢各大醫院，應用於新型冠狀病毒患者中「重症中的危重症患者」。他表示，目前沒有特效抗病毒藥物，治療以對症、支持為主。"},{"pid":"7d45b0f845ba6e11d0a8e4cc6efcaf6fda4e8fe9","tid":1833970,"uid":63157,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>目前沒有特效抗病毒藥物，治療以對症、支持為主。</strong><br />\n大咩結局? 吊命咋"},{"pid":"e235f2c8b0c4f5f98be0329ed7df958e88a9c6fd","tid":1833970,"uid":67294,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"原來換肺就搞掂，支那強項<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860e88fc0715bcceac874fa3805b519a99e77528","tid":1833970,"uid":292987,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"讓人體自身的肺能夠得到充分的治療和休息<br />\n都仲係靠個肺自己好翻"},{"pid":"bdd90d583e621cb6dbc40e3b61aa45c7a5cdbee6","tid":1833970,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"留名等睇個ECMO冇充份消毒，下個用嗰陣交叉感染，變超級病毒"},{"pid":"d2586f2598fdf4de6dc06927f7fed6a300d33c34","tid":1833970,"uid":121259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"ECMO全醫院應該唔係有好多部, 咁多人奶野, 夠用咩?"},{"pid":"411f7dd9662b0b8a52293d36b39d64fee6280c8e","tid":1833970,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d45b0f845ba6e11d0a8e4cc6efcaf6fda4e8fe9","tid":1833970,"uid":63157,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>目前沒有特效抗病毒藥物，治療以對症、支持為主。</strong><br />\n大咩結局? 吊命咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:40:27.000Z","msg":"sars當年咪又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da076d8de728afe23b5bd8be265e2717455be03f","tid":1833970,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"柯文哲咁中意&quot;友中&quot;,<br />\n快d 去武漢支援,向中共表達自己嘅善意啦!!"},{"pid":"eea5af22845e74a86c49cb0e43a6c7639422152c","tid":1833970,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"411f7dd9662b0b8a52293d36b39d64fee6280c8e","tid":1833970,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d45b0f845ba6e11d0